-- insert into table

declare @StartValue int;
set @StartValue=(select last_num from new_num where table_name = 'pr_emp_allowances_gen');

insert into pr_emp_allowances_gen([id],[emp_id],[emp_code],[fy],[fm],[m_id],[m_type],[amount],[active],[trans_id]) 
select @StartValue+ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY emp_code) AS Row,
[emp_id],[emp_code],[fy],[fm],[m_id],[m_type],[amount],[active],[trans_id] from pr_emp_allowances_gen_temp

declare @lastnum int;
set @lastnum = (select top 1 id from pr_emp_allowances_gen order by id desc)
update new_num set last_num=@lastnum where table_name='pr_emp_allowances_gen'






--drop
drop table pr_emp_deductions_temp;
